      id="bson_copy">
  <info>
    <link type="guide" xref="bson_t" group="function"/>
  </info>
  <title>bson_copy()</title>

  <section id="synopsis">
    <title>Synopsis</title>
    <synopsis><code mime="text/x-csrc"><![CDATA[bson_t *
bson_copy (const bson_t *bson);
]]></code></synopsis>
  </section>

  <section id="parameters">
    <title>Parameters</title>
    <table>
      <tr><td><p>bson</p></td><td><p>A <link xref="bson_t">bson_t</link>.</p></td></tr>
    </table>
  </section>

  <section id="description">
    <title>Description</title>
    <p>The <link xref="bson_copy">bson_copy()</link> function shall copy the contents of a bson document into a new <link xref="bson_t">bson_t</link>.</p>
    <p>The resulting <link xref="bson_t">bson_t</link> should be freed with <link xref="bson_destroy">bson_destroy()</link>.</p>
  </section>

  <section id="return">
    <title>Returns</title>
    <p>A newly allocated <link xref="bson_t">bson_t</link> that should be freed with <link xref="bson_destroy">bson_destroy()</link>.</p>
  </section>
</page>
